resp=\"#JP\">\n                \u003Cp>Gaius Iulis Felix lived for [--] years. Appuleia Rogata lived for [--] years\u003C/p>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"translation\" xml:lang=\"it\" resp=\"#JP\">\n                \u003Cp>Gaio Giulio Felice visse anni [--]. Appuleia Rogata visse anni [--]\u003C/p>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"commentary\">\n                \u003Cp>The absence of the ages for both individuals is unusual, and the best explanation is that the inscription was engraved before the death of the two and was never completed with their age of death. Theoretically, the age might have been added using paint, which has since been lost.\u003C/p>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"bibliography\">\n                \u003ClistBibl type=\"edition\">\n                    \u003Cbibl type=\"corpus\" n=\"CIL\">\n                        \u003Cauthor>Mommsen\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>1883\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>\n                            \u003Cref target=\"http://arachne.uni-koeln.de/item/buchseite/650810\">7512\u003C/ref>\n                        \u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/GQN8UZSI\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000589\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000589\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl type=\"corpus\" n=\"ILMusPalermo\">\n                         \u003Cauthor>Bivona\u003C/author>\n                         \u003Cdate>1970\u003C/date> \n                        \u003CcitedRange>6\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/FZWWPUD6\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002142\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002142\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl/>\n                \u003C/listBibl>\n\t   \u003ClistBibl type=\"discussion\">\u003Cbibl/>\u003C/listBibl>\n            \u003C/div>\n        \u003C/body>\n    \u003C/text>\n\u003C/TEI>\n"],"uses":{"params":["slug"]}}]}
